{"tid":1053212,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[你們的女神] 巨乳模指交加藤鷹！黃榕自爆只吃「大的」","createTime":"2019-03-09T00:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T02:44:35.000Z","uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a147519616ed1423c4c802eabef9d1d6d1d87dcf","tid":1053212,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T00:52:07.000Z","msg":"女星黃榕日前與日本殿堂級AV男優「神之手」加藤鷹出席活動，她更攬實加藤鷹自拍，相當興奮。她大讚加藤鷹非常有禮貌：「第一次見面佢主動同我握手，佢握手嘅力度好溫柔、溫暖，而且非常親切、笑容滿面，我仲專登帶咗本寫真送畀佢，佢好有禮貌即時睇完仲大讚我性感可愛！」 <br />\n<br />\n問到加藤鷹可是她喜歡的男性類型？她坦言喜歡男朋友一定要「大」：「唔係年紀大，係要有強大嘅手臂同胸膛，因為鍾意翹住男朋友手臂，同瞓喺男友胸膛，之前都有試過同日本男模拍拖，日本男仔真係非常溫柔同呵護體貼，不過依家我鍾意運動粗獷型男多啲。」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lkb2gkf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLkb2gkf.png&h=e5b316e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hs7XPFg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHs7XPFg.png&h=3183f3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ik6Yy6X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fik6Yy6X.png&h=cac1266e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XrNH0MX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXrNH0MX.png&h=92edb2fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6de088d86e4ae4653ec7e4ebde20e03e9498a0ee","tid":1053212,"uid":43575,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T00:56:13.000Z","msg":"好心咁老就咪走出黎出醜啦，你估個個都好似阿嬌keep 得咁好咩？"},{"pid":"de0a6502cbde9768eec27782d6d910f342bf78de","tid":1053212,"uid":37413,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T00:57:07.000Z","msg":"Who？"},{"pid":"6a56e0f1f48fc1b657f3c6aedb29287accc4dc1e","tid":1053212,"uid":3405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T00:57:58.000Z","msg":"留名睇v字腳"},{"pid":"92836a277c609964dcc052b70393a6f0481e484a","tid":1053212,"uid":17628,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T00:58:02.000Z